# Internet Simulator Demo Image

This is a placeholder "image" file for testing file transfer functionality.

In a real scenario, this would be binary image data (PNG, JPEG, etc.).

For the demo purposes, this text file simulates an image file that can be transferred between nodes.

The file transfer system handles:
- Binary data transmission
- Chunking and reassembly
- Error detection and correction
- TCP reliability features

File size: ~500 bytes (simulated small image)
Format: PNG (simulated)
Content: Demo data for network testing

This demonstrates that the simulator can handle any type of file content, not just text.
